<h3>Test Within Automations</h3>
<p>Most businesses set up automations and never touch them again. That is a mistake. A/B test one element per month in each active workflow:</p>
<ul>
<li>Subject lines (test 2 per email)</li>
<li>Send timing (morning vs. evening)</li>
<li>CTA text ("Shop now" vs. "See the collection")</li>
<li>Email length (short vs. detailed)</li>
<li>Incentive presence (discount vs. no discount)</li>
</ul>
<p>Run each test to statistical significance. 1,000+ recipients per variant minimum.</p>
